content.html: Sept 1990 "Hi Martin, when's the next Birmingham train?" "In 30 minutes if you can make it. Things going well with you and Sam?" "Yeah, brilliant. Last trip before we go off to Uni, Sam to Bristol, me to Cardiff. Won't be troubling you for a while." "You're no trouble Tom." 5/12
